Step 1: change wifi-credentials to your mobile hotspot such that your laptop and esp should connect to one common device which is your phone in this case.

Step 2: Flash espserver.ino code to esp8266

Step 3: Observe IP ADDRESS of esp on serial monitor inside ArdiunoIDE

Step 4: send a GET request from laptop to esp using curl or browser with its ip
	e.g. curl 192.168.223.145/on



Extra: Add any Digital analog pins to the if-else ladder,expand the functionality.
